{"title":"Dangerholm drops sub 10kg Hyper Spark XC dream bike w/ stratospheric spec list","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/09/dangerholm-drops-sub-10kg-hyper-spark-xc-dream-bike-w-stratospheric-spec-list/","date":1612888987000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Gustav Gullholm, aka Dangerholm, is back with another jaw dropping dream-bike build in the form of the pearl white Hyper Spark. A Scott Spark RC has been the focus of Gustav’s attention for the last two years. Fully integrated stealth cable routing, extremely lightweight components and electronic everything, the Hyper Spark is a dream bike build like no other.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post.jpg\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng%3Awebp%2Fngcb8%2Frs%3Adevice%2Frscb8-1\" alt=\"hyper spark dangerholm scott sparkrc white dream built schmolke carbon seat post\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post-696x464.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post-1068x712.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-rc-dangerholm-dream-build-pearl-white-super-lightweight-xc-bike-white-seat-post-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p>Dangerholm has garnered himself an outrageously large following on social media platforms after building the World’s Lightest Downhill Bike and the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/03/27/bfs2018-the-worlds-lightest-29er-mountain-bikes-are-a-scott-spark-scale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">World’s Lightest XC bikes</a>. How did he do it? He did something rather unimaginable with a Mora knife…</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation.jpg\" alt=\"scott spark rc carbon xc frame sanded dangerholm\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bi