sl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/dangerholm-snading-scott-spark-rc-hyper-spark-creation-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>Gustav took a very sharp knife to the production Spark and Scale frames, stripping them bare of heavy, unnecessary paint jobs. Now, Dangerholm is back again with another dream build of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/02/08/pro-bike-check-nino-schurter-kate-courtneys-new-2019-scott-spark-rc-race-bikes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">World Cup-winning</a> carbon Spark RC, named the Hyper Spark. In its lightest iteration, this pearl white full suspension XC bike weighs a svelte 9.78 kg. Let’s see what spec upgrades have allowed it.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit.jpg\" alt=\"scott hyper spark dangerholm build syncros fraser carbon bar integrated cable management stealth routing\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/scott-hyper-spark-dangerholm-white-build-cockpit-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Dangerholm’s Hyper Spark runs a Syncros Fraser iC SL carbon bar (cut to 730mm) for its sleek integrated aesthetic that allows for stealth cable management. Cables for brakes, shifters and Fox Live Valve suspension are all routed through the Syncros bar and down through the headset and steerer in a super neat fashion.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Scott-Sports_Hyper-Spark_Dangerholm_Steering-Stop-Wrapped24.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Scott-Sports_Hyper-Spark_Dangerholm_Steering-Stop-Wrapped24.jpg\" alt=\"dangerholm custom steering stop steerer tube cable protection hyper spark\" width=\"1200\" height=\"791\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng n